{"tid":615244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律jj入]點解係台灣殺人無事，係台灣講獨會有事","createTime":"2018-04-03T07:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T23:51:56.000Z","uid":64621,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41d64dfe3e7ebaea61cd21bac970b9d0052ac261","tid":615244,"uid":64621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"戴妖單野嘈咗好耐都係講緊講獨得唔得<br />\n但係有冇人留意佢係喺台灣講<br />\n香港幾時有咗台灣司法管轄權<br />\n咁殺人嗰單又攪唔掂？<br />\n最後有個法律問題問法律撚<br />\n如果炸迪迪尼單案係事主去台灣旅遊先出po<br />\n又真係有ip同出境紀錄證明佢事發係台灣<br />\n咁香港政府仲告唔告到佢<br />\n如果告到理由係咩？"},{"pid":"4b62354091cef4b02f29b207d333eec9df22e011","tid":615244,"uid":91152,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:51:17.000Z","msg":"最撚憎lawyer 根本當權者想點就點 呢班人只係趨炎附勢 歐美除外"},{"pid":"619b334a94460656c5475bf700ebbc20833d3a31","tid":615244,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66db67bba31e732432221ad925821261d10797f8","tid":615244,"uid":109102,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"搞批鬥邊關法律事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b7f3ed51b2c859168be7acfb7803507203757f","tid":615244,"uid":64621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66db67bba31e732432221ad925821261d10797f8","tid":615244,"uid":109102,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"搞批鬥邊關法律事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T07:54:21.000Z","msg":"人民日報唔係話刑事罪行條例適用咩？<br />\n佢講法律我跟佢講法律"},{"pid":"8aa36442c29bcfaea6d5c009e50fab3d02e72f33","tid":615244,"uid":64621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T21:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcd826df9d4baf0844529bf25e4793b0ffeb138","tid":615244,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T22:02:59.000Z","msg":"冇事架 依家文革批鬥咋嘛<br />\n又唔拉人"},{"pid":"f53e9f4687c4468c1b93f34a934a0c5ed63dd5b8","tid":615244,"uid":64621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cfcd826df9d4baf0844529bf25e4793b0ffeb138","tid":615244,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T22:02:59.000Z","msg":"冇事架 依家文革批鬥咋嘛<br />\n又唔拉人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T23:39:49.000Z","msg":"批鬥還批鬥<br />\n但係要拉要鎖唔該先講下香港幾時有台灣司法管轄權先<br />\n就算有23條都要證明戴妖係香港預謀去台灣講獨先有事<br />\n除非咩一國兩制，司法獨立，法治等等掉曬落垃圾桶<br />\n如果唔係我真係諗唔到點用香港法律規範係台灣所做嘅行為"},{"pid":"5afd8d2ea7968ea4c39c91a217c6eea8d458a219","tid":615244,"uid":35135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T23:51:56.000Z","msg":"好似話煽動香港境內嘅罪行，無論當時身處邊度都犯法，而殺人就單一事件，當地嘅犯罪，得台灣先拉得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然 戴 有冇煽動，討論嘅事有冇犯法就另一回事"}]}